title: Spud and Lettuce
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Healthy fast food concept with lots of veggie choices: rolls and wraps, meat free breakfast, jacket potatoes, salads, soups, hot drinks and smoothies. Free Wi-Fi. Vegans could get baked beans and sweet potato, chickpea and spinach baked potato fillings, breakfast food. Est. 2015.
